NOOB-FRIENDLY:

  1. Go to Java’s Website and Download JDK 6 From the link below:

    (The first download on the page)

  2. Go to tutorial section: http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/board,51.0.html

  3. Open NotePad.exe, Paste the ‘perfect’ compiler on there and save it as “Compiler.bat”

  4. Download a Source at the download’s section: http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/board,49.0.html

  5. Read: http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,37596.0.html

Have Fun. Please correct your Grammer etc. It’s very hard for people to understand what you’re trying to say.
